DefaultInput.ini
 = UDK/UDK-2014-05/UDKGame/Config

UTPawn.uc
 = UDK/UDK-2014-05/Development/Src/UTGame/Classes

***************************IMPORTANT***************************

Place files in respective paths. Replace old versions.
Delete both UDKInput.ini and UDKGame.ini, then run the editor.
The engine will generate new UDK files from DefaultInput with 
the new keybindings.

